  <body>
    <p>
      关闭Quicker
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">如果您需要关闭Quicker，可以在弹开面板后，打开菜单，点“关闭”菜单项。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1616398769669-18634082-56ed-4a52-8c7a-bf581b13c8cb.png" class="ne-image" width="439" height="311" style="width: 439px; height: 311px;"/>
      
