<node ID="ID_869040643" CREATED="1754214185253" MODIFIED="1754215383612"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      动作页加载规则
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">如果为当前软件添加了“场景”设置并创建了动作页，则加载此场景的动作页。</span>
