      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2019/png/272392/1564210230783-752d4e3b-22e7-44bd-8c3d-c3e3d8c454d5.png" width="24" class="ne-image"/>
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2019/png/272392/1564210279977-5751beb6-e102-4f42-bf72-c51a256111b9.png" width="24" class="ne-image"/>
      <strong><span class="ne-text">锁定面板：</span></strong><span class="ne-text">暂时停止自动切换上下文面板区域的动作页。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2019/png/272392/1564210300913-90b0f8ee-ff5c-4bde-8d24-baf9112e3ebb.png" width="24" class="ne-image"/>
      <strong><span class="ne-text">工具窗口菜单：</span></strong>
