<node ID="ID_464056313" CREATED="1754214185277" MODIFIED="1754231259793"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      钉住面板
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">如果你希望Quicker面板一直悬浮在桌面上不自动隐藏，可以使用“钉住”功能。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2019/png/272392/1552833118504-a0fca3b6-64c2-41fe-a024-f44db1d121ca.png" class="ne-image" width="370" height="89" style="width: 370px; height: 89px;"/>
      
