<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">不得含有任何恶意内容；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">有较为详细的说明文档：</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">动作实现的功能、使用场景；</span>
        </li>
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">如何使用动作的说明；</span>
        </li>
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">动作应设置合适的关键词（仅设置具有强关联的）；</span>
        </li>
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">建议提供演示动画，方便更直观的了解；</span>
        </li>
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">应设置合适的应用程序关联和动作分类</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
        <ul ne-level="2" class="ne-ul">
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">避免将动作关联到不密切相关的应用程序上；</span>
          </li>
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">关联到<code class="ne-code">通用</code>场景时，应选择1个合适的分类。</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">应尽量通用</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">避免用户需要修改后才能使用动作；</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
        <ul ne-level="2" class="ne-ul">
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">特殊情况下，必须进行编辑的，在动作网页中增加修改说明；</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">如果有需要配置的参数，请参考 </span><a href="https://getquicker.net/KC/Help/Doc/store-settings" target="_blank"><span class="ne-bookmark-inline">在动作中存储用户设置 - Quicker</span></a><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;实现配置保存；</span>
        </li>
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">应避免这些情况：</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
        <ul ne-level="2" class="ne-ul">
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">使用特定文件路径（可能其他人电脑上不存在，导致动作失效）；</span>
          </li>
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">使用自定义的快捷键；</span>
          </li>
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">依赖本地资源（如找图本地文件）；</span>
          </li>
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">依赖特定分辨率；</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">特定场景、内部使用的动作，也请非公开方式分享；</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">应确保安全</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">动作中下载外部组件、文件的；</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
        <ul ne-level="2" class="ne-ul">
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">应该加以声明；</span>
          </li>
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">有下载exe等可执行程序的，应加以突出说明，且文件应通过VirusTotal等网站扫描病毒，确认安全后再分享，以免造成较大损失；</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">动作中有删除、更改文件的，请详细测试确保安全后再分享，以避免造成他人严重损失；</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">减少重复动作</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">避免公开分享和已有动作功能和实现基本相同的动作，以减少动作库的重复动作；</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
        <ul ne-level="2" class="ne-ul">
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">功能相同，实现思路更优的不受影响；</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">在其它动作基础上修改的动作</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
        <ul ne-level="2" class="ne-ul">
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">应尊重原作者的授权；</span>
          </li>
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">仅在有较大改进时再分享，以避免动作库重复；</span>
          </li>
          <li data-lake-index-type="0">
            <span class="ne-text">应在动作网页中详细说明相对于原始动作所做的改进；</span>
