<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p data-lake-id="3fc475395df788f2cf19624b6afe6b3a">
      也可以在要添加黑名单的软件上弹出面板后，点击添加黑名单的按钮。（只对未设置过动作页的软件生效）
    </p>
    <p data-lake-id="0f09602889b0d11cc8720a99bea269a4">
      <span data-card-type="inline" data-lake-card="image" class="lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom"><img loading="lazy" data-role="image" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1616821484084-5a99d0c6-e65c-473c-9ed5-9a96a5baf3bb.png" data-raw-src="" class="image lake-drag-image" alt="160647_3_mceclip2.png" title="160647_3_mceclip2.png" data-height="145px"/>
