<node ID="ID_1405176578" CREATED="1754214283283" MODIFIED="1754215383663"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      根据主题自动切换面板和轮盘外观
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">在外观设置中开启 “<strong>根据主题自动切换外观设置</strong>”后，可以设置两套外观，并且实现在切换主题自动加载，从而实现面板和轮盘外观的自动变化。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/gif/272392/1694140243737-c4b2f79f-5389-435f-a2e3-d308c9f3956d.gif" width="1079" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">为深色模式设置面板和轮盘外观：</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">1）开启“根据主题自动切换外观设置”选项；</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">2）在“深色主题设置”标签页中设置外观参数。也可以点击“预置风格”按钮，选择“深色”，加载默认的深色主题。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/png/272392/1694137237797-729557fc-8a2a-4d87-86e2-581493bd5433.png" width="903.3333333333334" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">3）在轮盘外观设置中，切换到深色主题模式后，可调配轮盘深色模式外观。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">点击“恢复默认轮盘外观”，可以加载预置的深色轮盘配色。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/gif/272392/1694137076797-1f1aab6b-62ae-4a2e-a95f-02e4c92e8953.gif" width="770.6666666666666" class="ne-image"/>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_1663340047" CREATED="1754214283286" MODIFIED="1754215383664"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      通过动作切换模式
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">可以根据需要，在组合动作中切换主题模式或者获取当前主题模式的信息。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">通过 “Quicker操作”可以切换主题到指定模式。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/png/272392/1693298985391-a1341ca1-df23-436c-9394-6ec5270461f3.png" width="850" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">通过“获取系统和动作信息”模块，可以得到当前Windows和Quicker所使用的主题模式。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/png/272392/1693298931693-dd6729e0-d198-4b1a-8020-644c4e731767.png" width="850" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">Windows是否位为深色模式返回布尔值，深色时为true。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">Quicker主题模式返回文本值：</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">light：浅色模式</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">dark：深色模式</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">auto_light：跟随Windows，并且当前windows为浅色模式。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">auto_dark：跟随Windows，并且当前为深色模式。</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
