        <a href="https://www.windows10.pro/run-command-to-open-the-uwp-application/" data-href="https://www.windows10.pro/run-command-to-open-the-uwp-application/" target="_blank"><span class="ne-text">https://www.windows10.pro/run-command-to-open-the-uwp-application/</span></a><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;&#xa0;巧用命令快速打开Win10 UWP应用（附常用UWP应用运行命令）</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.tenforums.com/tutorials/78214-settings-pages-list-uri-shortcuts-windows-10-a.html" data-href="https://www.tenforums.com/tutorials/78214-settings-pages-list-uri-shortcuts-windows-10-a.html" target="_blank"><span class="ne-text">https://www.tenforums.com/tutorials/78214-settings-pages-list-uri-shortcuts-windows-10-a.html</span></a><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;Win10设置页面URI汇总</span>
