<node ID="ID_1078233177" CREATED="1754214363026" MODIFIED="1754215383688"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      设置要触发的操作
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">在空白位置点击鼠标左键或右键，即可为此位置创建动作。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/webp/272392/1642601132606-f7d89a90-a80a-4c62-9261-99089a3ce77c.webp" width="887.3333333333334" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">触发的具体操作的设置，请参考：<a href="https://getquicker.net/KC/Manual/Doc/quick-actions" data-href="https://getquicker.net/KC/Manual/Doc/quick-actions" target="_blank">https://www.yuque.com/quicker/help/quick-actions</a></span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">如果要触发Quicker动作，也可以从动作页/面板窗口中拖放到轮盘上。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2019/gif/272392/1576125161368-c18b60e0-3a69-47b1-b26c-1e0c2f1271af.gif" width="1214" class="ne-image"/>
      
