<node ID="ID_1355321515" CREATED="1754214363047" MODIFIED="1754215383692"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      常见问题FAQ
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">Q：如何禁用轮盘功能？</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">A: 在<a href="https://getquicker.net/KC/Manual/Doc/settings-circlemenusettingpage" data-href="settings-circlemenusettingpage">轮盘菜单设置页</a>中将触发键选项中选择“-无-”即可。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">Q：如何在某个特定的软件中禁用轮盘？</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">在要禁用轮盘的程序场景中选中“在此软件下禁用轮盘菜单”选项。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1642642394762-94edaace-44ee-4faf-9d25-c90f812cccc5.png" width="707.3333333333334" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">Q：如何仅在某些软件中启用轮盘？</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">如果希望默认不开启轮盘，可以在“全局”场景中选择“默认禁用轮盘”选项，然后在各程序场景中选择开启或关闭轮盘功能。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1642642634620-cae49877-603f-4f06-8acf-03b2ef222adb.png" width="734" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">Q：如何让外圈显示16格？</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">需要是专业版，然后在轮盘设置中开启即可。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1642642897017-a87f97a1-907a-4f6a-b53c-62eadbc987e6.png" width="778.6666666666666" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">Q：为什么我轮盘最外面（第三圈）显示不出来？</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">最外圈（扩展圈）是超出轮盘时才触发的 ；需要先设置好对应位置的动作；</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">Q：如何不叠加全局场景的动作</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">如果不希望使用叠加方式显示每个位置的动作，可以通过高级鼠标触发轮盘，并设置场景名称为<code class="ne-code">_curr</code></span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">1）关闭轮盘中的触发鼠标键。<br/></span><img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2024/png/272392/1720580664028-0e3e3b73-21ca-4fdf-9375-2a3c0f56b455.png" width="602" class="ne-image"/>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">2）在高级鼠标触发中添加规则。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2024/png/272392/1720580670274-4c14736b-f9ad-440e-87d3-e4272626a0c1.png" width="522" class="ne-image"/>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
