    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">快速搜索Windows软件或指定目录中的绿色软件。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1656655269477-af3a6cf0-66f7-4401-ac1c-ef7f576750dc.png" class="ne-image" width="663" height="627" style="width: 663px; height: 627px;"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">参数：</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li>
        <p>
          <span class="ne-text">索引</span><code>PATH</code><span class="ne-text">环境变量中的路径：自动索引系统PATH环境变量里保存的目录路径中的程序文件。</span>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <span class="ne-text">绿色软件文件夹：设定要索引的自定义目录。</span>
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <li>
        <p>
          <span class="ne-text">每行一个路径，格式为</span><code>目录路径|扫描深度</code><span class="ne-text">。扫描深度为0时表示不扫描该目录的子目录。</span>
        </p>
