  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      电源状态改变了
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">当电脑休眠/睡眠或唤醒的时候触发事件。对应于<a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/microsoft.win32.systemevents.powermodechanged?view=netframework-4.7.2" data-href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/microsoft.win32.systemevents.powermodechanged?view=netframework-4.7.2" target="_blank">SystemEvents.PowerModeChanged</a>事件。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">触发条件参数：无</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">输出参数</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/png/272392/1676124844718-e2dcbc9e-39cc-46c6-a92b-5920cbb06f2f.png" width="360" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">【模式】</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li>
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Resume</span></code><span class="ne-text">系统唤醒。</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Suspend</span></code><span class="ne-text">系统即将睡眠/休眠。</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">StatusChange</span></code><span class="ne-text">系统电源事件通知。可能是电池电力不足/开始充电，插入或断开了电源线，或其它电源事件。</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">【PowerLineStatus】电源线连接状态。本参数和下面的几个是通过<a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.windows.forms.powerstatus.batterychargestatus?view=windowsdesktop-7.0" data-href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.windows.forms.powerstatus.batterychargestatus?view=windowsdesktop-7.0" target="_blank">SystemInformation.PowerStatus</a>获得的。</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">0：未连接</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">1：已连接</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">255：未知状态</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">【BatteryChargeStatus】充电状态。请参考<a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.windows.forms.batterychargestatus?view=windowsdesktop-7.0" data-href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.windows.forms.batterychargestatus?view=windowsdesktop-7.0" target="_blank">这里</a></span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">【BatteryLifePercent】电池剩余电量比例。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">【BatteryLifeRemaining】电池预计剩余时间（秒数）。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">【BatteryFullLifetime】电池满电预计寿命（秒数）。</span>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
