    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2019/png/272392/1554100073892-c4bf9d49-2618-41ba-9446-c233cca93057.png" width="355" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">也可以在打开的动作信息窗口中点击动作ID：</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2019/png/272392/1554087547420-117dc3b1-6388-41d3-8bb6-4d4c83a22853.png" width="364" class="ne-image"/>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
