            </li>
            <li data-lake-id="24b24bcf023789854855ddbea1c73f62">
              双击或点动作后面的<span data-card-type="inline" data-lake-card="image"><img loading="lazy" data-role="image" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1585784778705-e03c0d55-d60f-488f-bd2c-c1d0930c8cfd.png" data-raw-src="" class="image lake-drag-image" alt="image.png" title="image.png" data-height="10px"/></span>可以更新单个动作。
