<node ID="ID_262102574" CREATED="1754213378614" MODIFIED="1754214745164" LINK="https://getquicker.net/KC/Manual/Doc/web-action-list"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      动作单
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="article-content js-toc-content">
        <div class="p-2 text-secondary bg-light mb-2">
          因软件更新较快，部分文档内容与软件最新版本有所出入，请知悉。
        </div>
        <h1>
          概述
        </h1>
        <p data-lake-id="a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">可以把动作单看作音乐软件中的“歌单”。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="1eb7b6e783bad1f25894c62d96f23f7c">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">动作单分为“<strong>隐私</strong>”动作单和“<strong>公开</strong>”动作单。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="2762882e7d772aff041d929843e2c667">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">隐私动作单：仅自己可见。可以在任何时候转换为为公开动作单。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="1afe0382d783dc2f00e84fe21fcfb7a9">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">公开动作单：所有人可见。其他用户可以“收藏”公开动作单。公开动作单</span><strong>不可以</strong><span class="lake-fontsize-11">转换为隐私动作单。</span>
        </p>
        <h1>
          创建动作单
        </h1>
        <h2>
          方法1：在收藏动作页面中创建
        </h2>
        <p data-lake-id="f4ee08dba53b9ac4daa27c46bf917b6b">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">步骤：</span>
        </p>
        <ol start="1">
          <li>
            <span class="lake-fontsize-11">登录到Quicker网站。</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="lake-fontsize-11">在动作页面中点击右侧的“+ 收藏”按钮。</span><br/><img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589166321754-d2ae024b-4d8e-45dc-94a8-ef3ff39d4109.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=178&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=356&amp;originWidth=414&amp;size=16150&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=207"/>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="lake-fontsize-11">在弹出的窗口中，点击“+ 创建动作单”按钮。</span><br/><img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589166385557-28cbe6e2-e81d-422e-ac7f-713122ed0617.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=200&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=400&amp;originWidth=1011&amp;size=31738&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=505.5"/>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="lake-fontsize-11">输入动作单信息，选择是否为隐私动作单后点击“创建动作单”按钮即可。</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <h2>
          方法2：在动作单列表页面中创建
        </h2>
        <p data-lake-id="8e93bf0e76dc4cf793f4415223bc05d1">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">步骤：</span>
        </p>
        <ol start="1">
          <li>
            <span class="lake-fontsize-11">打开动作单网页（动作库-&gt;动作单）：<a href="https://getquicker.net/Share/ActionLists" target="_blank">https://getquicker.net/Share/ActionLists</a></span><br/><img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589166511438-d1175ad9-faf7-4b38-add9-9feef4094c0c.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=130&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=260&amp;originWidth=1734&amp;size=50727&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=867"/>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="lake-fontsize-11">点击“创建动作单”按钮。</span><br/><img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589166763082-e3f51c48-7dad-4866-9ace-6b44a7ab90e4.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=291&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=581&amp;originWidth=750&amp;size=53484&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=375"/>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="lake-fontsize-11">在接下来的页面中创建即可。</span><br/><img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589167059060-dc213f7c-6180-4c7c-ac43-a51bff74f6a8.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=361&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=722&amp;originWidth=953&amp;size=51694&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=476.5"/>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <h1>
          收藏动作
        </h1>
        <p data-lake-id="d73e1746030191b07e2a0c039ec1987c">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">在动作页面中点击“收藏”按钮，点击要收藏到的动作单名称，输入可选的简单评价内容后保存即可。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="c4fe36e191f817ef0f71273db913d7e0">
          <img loading="lazy" alt="动作单_收藏动作.gif" title="动作单_收藏动作.gif" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/gif/272392/1589167766766-c6870c67-77c3-4c8a-8746-de1656a7bc85.gif#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=389&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%8D%95_%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C.gif&amp;originHeight=690&amp;originWidth=1508&amp;size=413188&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=851"/>
          
        </p>
        <h1>
          收藏动作单
        </h1>
        <p data-lake-id="4540129492d52cc2e0a4e80d7117bcc3">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">进入动作单后，点击“收藏”按钮即可收藏此动作单。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="cd413933e2e958e09c7a4180d84fd773">
          <img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589168606057-f3e4285d-cb69-464b-9026-2568bf3af94f.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=167&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=333&amp;originWidth=1775&amp;size=49547&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=887.5"/>
          
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="36eaea9bc394a134ae4cb725a45d4235">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">动作单列表中，自己收藏的动作单前面会显示星标。也可以在左侧选择“我的收藏”查看所有收藏的动作单。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="141993b72a5983945887d9f1656dc192">
          <img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589168714958-8dac0457-1edf-4abb-86af-d7d4648aeadc.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=222&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=444&amp;originWidth=1737&amp;size=111395&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=868.5"/>
          
        </p>
        <h1>
          管理动作单
        </h1>
        <p data-lake-id="37dcfb25ecf892e3ea158922b1c6410f">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">在动作单列表网页（<a href="https://getquicker.net/Share/ActionLists?tab=my" target="_blank">https://getquicker.net/Share/ActionLists?tab=my</a>）中点击要管理的动作单。</span>
        </p>
        <h2>
          修改动作单信息
        </h2>
        <p data-lake-id="db5a60891313959ceb0be1d9cc2fbe5c">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">点击右侧的“设置”按钮，进入动作单设置页面。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="9df4f5de258555915bbb5f1a2327127b">
          <img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589168269176-edae6b8e-2f35-4135-b387-f7934b1c1225.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=174&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=348&amp;originWidth=1474&amp;size=58492&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=737"/>
          
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="081c2bc14d9bbbe8639650302d9cfbf8">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">可以修改动作单名称/说明等信息，或将隐私动作单修改为公开动作单。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="96a6daa6aba2bfdbee2cf7a88ee6a174">
          <img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589168291006-bd1b191f-29d1-4ee1-9871-0ff5a9188d4d.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=373&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=746&amp;originWidth=1502&amp;size=73741&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=751"/>
          
        </p>
        <h2>
          移除动作
        </h2>
        <p data-lake-id="542501ae2b050f2f70f8abced6dce652">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">点击动作名称后的X，可以将动作从动作单中移除。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="1ef9b41eb13926c26cff4c6d50df6723">
          <img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589168388187-323e1f73-fcc7-40f9-88c4-ee351e3b5d49.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=217&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=434&amp;originWidth=1151&amp;size=73845&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=575.5"/>
          
        </p>
        <h2>
          修改简评文字
        </h2>
        <p data-lake-id="8bbb06f38f7a1a17e165ae4ad9867a76">
          <span class="lake-fontsize-11">点击动作名称后面的编辑按钮，可以修改动作的简评信息。</span>
        </p>
        <p data-lake-id="e3c196c4b04cb1155608bbc237cb4d26">
          <img loading="lazy" alt="image.png" title="image.png" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589168483388-72b12ba9-2f7d-4c93-8fa1-1e06fd1e1784.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=230&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=460&amp;originWidth=1013&amp;size=70133&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=506.5"/>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
