    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">组合动作编辑器窗口分为左中右三列。</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">左侧为模块工具箱</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">中间为动作步骤定义区域</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">右侧为变量定义和外观设置区域。</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1582003944030-3247b1f5-9b87-4813-a654-f48a80ed4104.png" width="776.5" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">基本的操作过程为：</span>
    </p>
    <ol class="ne-ol">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">定义要使用的变量；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">从模块工具箱中选取需要的模块，拖放到动作步骤列表中，并设置模块的输入和输出参数；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">调整外观（图标和文字标签）；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">保存。</span>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
