      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">d</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;或 <code class="ne-code">delete</code>&#xa0;删除选中步骤；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">e</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;编辑选中步骤；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">h</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;在步骤列表中按<code class="ne-code">h</code>高亮相同模块的步骤；在变量列表中按<code class="ne-code">h</code>高亮使用此变量的步骤（1.42.12+）；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Ctrl+F</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;定位到模块筛选框；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">/</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;在选择的步骤前面快速插入注释模块（1.28.5+）；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">F5</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;延迟2秒后调试运行动作（自动最小化编辑窗口）；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Ctrl+F5</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;延迟2秒后运行动作（自动最小化编辑窗口）；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">F6</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;立即调试运行动作 (1.30.4+)；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Ctrl+F6</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;立即运行动作；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">F2</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;对循环和判断步骤：展开或折叠；对运行子程序步骤：打开对应的子程序编辑界面；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Ctrl+G</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;将选择的步骤放入“步骤组”(1.40.25+)；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Ctrl+I</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;将选择的步骤放入“如果/否则”(1.40.25+)；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Ctrl+Shift+I</span></code><span class="ne-text">&#xa0;将选择的步骤放入“如果”(1.41.3+)；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Ctrl+R</span></code><span class="ne-text">将选择的步骤放入“重复”(1.40.25+)；</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <code class="ne-code"><span class="ne-text">Alt+↑</span></code><span class="ne-text">将选中的步骤上移一行，<code class="ne-code">Alt+↓</code>将选中的步骤下移一行 (1.42.14)，</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
