    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">在“列表”参数中，通过表达式 <code class="ne-code">$= {表格}.Rows</code>传入DataRow的集合。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1640158366536-7c627513-1109-417f-9622-dcf96f1c1c3f.png" width="628.5" class="ne-image"/>
      
