    <pre data-language="csharp" class="ne-codeblock language-csharp">{3+3=} 输出“6”
{DateTime.Now.ToString(&quot;yyyy-MM-dd&quot;)=}</pre>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">示例动作：<a href="https://getquicker.net/sharedaction?code=aa38d2b9-f95b-4a91-d713-08d827485760" data-href="https://getquicker.net/sharedaction?code=aa38d2b9-f95b-4a91-d713-08d827485760" target="_blank">https://getquicker.net/sharedaction?code=aa38d2b9-f95b-4a91-d713-08d827485760</a></span>
    </p>
