    <p>
      启用表达式
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">在输入框的开始处写<strong>$= </strong>（且只在开始处写）作为启用表达式的开关，后面写表达式的内容。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1578992316612-d4eb87d3-15b8-44f4-86df-54260b08e080.png" width="225.5" class="ne-image"/>
    </p>
