<node FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1855419183" CREATED="1754227587555" MODIFIED="1754229769261"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      概述
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">发送指定的按键序列到目标窗口。</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">本功能在内部使用了C#的&#xa0;<a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.windows.forms.sendkeys?view=netframework-4.8" data-href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.windows.forms.sendkeys?view=netframework-4.8" target="_blank">System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys.SendWait()</a>&#xa0;函数。因此，参数格式可以直接参考该文档。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
