    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">此模块和“<a href="https://getquicker.net/kc/help/doc/keyinput" data-href="https://getquicker.net/kc/help/doc/keyinput" target="_blank">模拟按键A（录入）</a>”模块的区别为：</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
