  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      屏幕坐标
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1623940291333-f635540e-ac33-4a69-b1b2-71001894c177.png" width="568" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">主屏幕的左上角为原点，X=0, Y=0。多屏幕时，主屏的左上角为原点。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">X表示水平坐标，向右为正值增加。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">Y表示垂直坐标，向下为正值增加。</span>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
