    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">当窗口位置或尺寸可能会变化，但是目标位置相对于窗口是固定的，可使用本功能。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">可选的参考点类型：</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">窗口左上角</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">窗口右上角</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">窗口左下角</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">窗口右下角</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">窗口中心</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2025/png/272392/1737336723305-5a5467a7-3e94-41b3-802b-d042c4473949.png" width="850" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">【X】和【Y】参数</span>
