      <span class="ne-text">单选时，输出内容为选择选项值文本；多选时，输出内容为选择选项值的列表。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1589326832473-3ca2aae6-cc14-43ec-8693-60d21beb867b.png" width="598" class="ne-image"/>
