        <span class="ne-text">Alt+↓ 将当前行向下移动一行</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">Ctrl+D 重复当前选中内容，未选择时重复当前行 (v1.40.12+)</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">Ctrl+Shift+D 删除当前行</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
