      概述
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">显示一个可以同时修改多个变量的表单窗口。如下图所示：</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1657506334191-aeb994c2-cd9f-4766-9d42-69b0d245848b.png" width="500" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">表单的每一行称为一个“<strong>字段</strong>”。每个字段用于修改一个变量的值或词典变量的某个键的值。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">表单显示的时候，会自动加载变量的当前值。表单保存后将输入的值写入到变量中。</span>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
<node ID="ID_1942496993" CREATED="1754227614002" MODIFIED="1754229769314"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      工作模式
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">【编辑动作变量的值】</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">用于编辑动作的某一些变量的值。显示表单时，会自动加载变量的当前值。表单保存后，会将修改后的值保存到变量。通常用于结合“作为状态使用”的变量，为动作创建<a href="https://getquicker.net/KC/Help/Doc/store-settings" data-href="https://getquicker.net/KC/Help/Doc/store-settings" target="_blank">设置界面</a>。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">【编辑词典数据】</span></strong><span class="ne-text">（<em>自1.34.5版本增加。</em>）</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">用于修改词典变量的内部数据（某些键所对应的值）。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">词典中需要事先存在表单中需要编辑的键值对。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1657591249524-3ef2f34b-4345-42a2-b554-fd4118214fd4.png" width="838" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">【编辑词典数据（动态）】</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">在动作运行期间动态生成表单定义。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">词典中需要事先存在表单中需要编辑的键值对。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1657591381384-c6c99f1e-07d1-49ac-82bc-a5dcc8dc47e8.png" width="838" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_473580454" CREATED="1754227614004" MODIFIED="1754229769314"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

