<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">1.5.7 增加提示文字参数。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">1.34.5 增加分组、编辑词典内容等功能。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
