<node FOLDED="true" ID="ID_20997094" CREATED="1754227288084" MODIFIED="1754227614067" LINK="https://getquicker.net/KC/Help/Doc/textselecttools"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      辅助选择工具
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">用于选取某项内容并得到对应的文本值。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1634568003432-c782ea8c-fc33-43af-9170-fa54a95a0505.png" width="628.5" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">功能类似于“表单”窗口或“用户输入”窗口的“文本选择工具”：</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1634568117677-048325fa-da0a-42ad-b578-34ed3e40fdd0.png" width="536" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">只是不再显示表单界面，而是直接显示选取界面开始选取。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">目前支持的选择工具如下：</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取文件... - SelectSingleFile</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取(多个)文件... - SelectMultiFile</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取文件夹... - SelectSingleFolder</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选择保存路径... - SelectSavePath</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选择窗口的进程路径。 - SelectProcessPath</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选择进程名 - SelectProcessName</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选择场景标识 - SelectProfileExe</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选择窗口句柄 - SelectWindowHandle</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">从键盘输入键名 - SelectKeyName</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">从键盘输入模拟按键B的内容 - SelectSendKeysData</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">从键盘输入键码数字 - SelectKeyCode</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取区域 - SelectLocationArea</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取坐标位置 - SelectLocationPoint</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取窗口坐标位置 - SelectRelativePoint</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">截图并获取路径 - CaptureToFile</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取矢量图标 - SelectIcon</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取动作ID - SelectActionId</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选取动作名称 - SelectActionName</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">选择窗口控件，获取其XPath - SelectControlXPath</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">已配对的蓝牙设备 - SelectBluetoothDevice</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">低功耗蓝牙设备 - SelectBluetoothLEDevice</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="ne-text">网络连接 - SelectNetworkProfile</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
