            <span class="ne-text">2009-06-15T13:45:30 (DateTimeKind.Local) -&gt; 2009-06-15T13:45:30<br/><br/>2009-06-15T13:45:30 (DateTimeKind.Utc) -&gt; 2009-06-15T13:45:30</span>
          </p>
        </td>
