        </td>
        <td width="250">
          <p class="ne-p">
            <span class="ne-text">短时间模式。<br/><br/>更多信息：<a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/dotnet/standard/base-types/standard-date-and-time-format-strings#ShortTime" data-href="https://learn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/dotnet/standard/base-types/standard-date-and-time-format-strings#ShortTime" target="_blank">短时间（“t”）格式说明符</a></span>
          </p>
          <p class="ne-p">
            <span class="ne-text">。</span>
          </p>
        </td>
        <td width="398">
          <p class="ne-p">
            <span class="ne-text">2009-06-15T13:45:30 -&gt; 1:45 PM (en-US)<br/><br/>2009-06-15T13:45:30 -&gt; 13:45 (hr-HR)<br/><br/>2009-06-15T13:45:30 -&gt; 01:45 م (ar-EG)</span>
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
