<node ID="ID_1397349335" CREATED="1754227687521" MODIFIED="1754229769491"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      一、通过文本窗口显示
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/gif/272392/1678544255384-66ad279b-cb2f-4226-aa53-731b88ba6f3e.gif" width="710.6666666666666" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">实现方法：</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/png/272392/1678544320775-f8e6195c-6b41-406f-a631-743739e06c6c.png" width="497.3333333333333" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">1）事先创建一个以非等待模式显示的文本窗口，设置窗口标识（建议使用‘=’作为窗口标识，相当于动作ID，以避免动作之间冲突）。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/png/272392/1678543877109-da331c37-3d34-4867-8b56-754c01530447.png" width="838" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">2）在AI调用模块中，启用流式输出和输出的文本窗口标识。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2023/png/272392/1678543990497-bf8b43be-6c63-4b99-b61d-87347387afb6.png" width="832" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">这样当收到新的内容后，会将内容追加到窗口中。</span>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
