<node ID="ID_1598733091" CREATED="1754227687546" MODIFIED="1754229769501"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      如何从浏览器获取请求头或Cookie
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">获取Cookie</span></strong>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">方法1：使用动作 <a href="https://getquicker.net/Sharedaction?code=bbf0a162-6f95-46fb-1e7a-08dbbf546dec" data-href="https://getquicker.net/Sharedaction?code=bbf0a162-6f95-46fb-1e7a-08dbbf546dec" target="_blank">https://getquicker.net/Sharedaction?code=bbf0a162-6f95-46fb-1e7a-08dbbf546dec</a></span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">方法2：按下面的方式找到请求头中的Cookie内容并复制。</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">获取Http请求头</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
