        <span class="ne-text">工作簿 = Workbook：对应于一个Excel文档。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">工作表 = Worksheet = Sheet：对应于Excel文档中的一个表。如下图中Excel文档包含Sheet1、Sheet2、Sheet3三个工作表。<br/></span><img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2022/png/272392/1649123899443-1f26b0e5-f9e3-4ee2-ba99-0b45fec83bef.png" width="380" title="" crop="0,0,1,1" class="ne-image"/>
      </li>
    </ul>
