<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2020/png/272392/1592985476740-297c3eac-6a47-485c-950f-835a2145bb3e.png" width="592" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">在【格式】参数中设定格式内容，每行一个，形式为“格式名称=格式值”。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">支持的格式如下：</span>
    </p>
    <table class="ne-table">
      <tr>
