    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2024/png/272392/1709509346999-238592c6-7401-4647-b33b-4fd6564c7be9.png" width="488" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">（2）必要时，使用表单窗口等用户界面步骤，请用户修改变量的值：</span></strong>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">判断变量的值不合法时，如变量中未存储程序路径或路径不合法。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">用户通过右键菜单启动了设置界面。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">判断发现用户启动动作时按住了<code class="ne-code">Ctrl</code>键等。</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
