<node ID="ID_1242382677" CREATED="1754229006635" MODIFIED="1754229769611"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      简单表达式与复杂表达式
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">简单表达式：</span></strong><span class="ne-text">相当于一个C#赋值语句的等号后面的部分。例如：</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">返回变量值加1的结果：<code class="ne-code">$= {数字变量} +1</code></span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">判断变量值是否大于10：<code class="ne-code">$= {数字变量} &gt; 10</code></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">复杂表达式：</span></strong><span class="ne-text">相当于一个返回特定内容的C#方法。例如：判断两个数字之中的较大值：</span>
    </p>
    <pre data-language="csharp" class="ne-codeblock language-csharp">$= 
if ({number1} &gt; {number2})
{
&#x9;return &quot;较大值为number1:&quot; + {number1};
}else{
&#x9;return &quot;较大值为number2:&quot; + {number2};
}</pre>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
