  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      表达式补全提示与验证
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">
<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">补全功能用于自动提示关键词、变量所支持的方法等内容。</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/gif/272392/1626305969438-468b51c2-f51d-40d8-8951-bb1c113942e1.gif" width="905" class="ne-image"/>
      
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">注意事项：</span></strong>
    </p>
    <ul class="ne-ul">
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">补全功能在服务器端实现，需要您的电脑能正常访问网络。</span>
      </li>
      <li data-lake-index-type="0">
        <span class="ne-text">补全内容与验证提示仅供参考。</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="ne-list-wrap">
      <ul ne-level="1" class="ne-ul">
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">表达式引擎不是一个完整的C#环境，有些补全提示的方法或关键词在表达式中不支持。</span>
        </li>
        <li data-lake-index-type="0">
          <span class="ne-text">有一些在表达式中可以使用的类型，没有对应的补全提示。</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">开启补全：</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <img loading="lazy" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1626308895473-2d9573cc-de37-4b1d-819d-c4befbc7bbc4.png" width="692.5" class="ne-image"/>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
