    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <strong><span class="ne-text">格式2，使用自定义颜色：[fa:图标名:#RRGGBB]</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">如：[<strong>fa:</strong>Solid_Pen<strong>:#FF0000</strong>]</span>
    </p>
    <p class="ne-p">
      <span class="ne-text">给图标设定固定的颜色值，格式为#RRGGBB。</span>
    </p>
