    </p>
    <p data-lake-id="c202595a47f41eaf74120c2225fb88d3">
      下面的例子是在运行动作时通过表单选择形状并输入尺寸信息：
    </p>
    <p data-lake-id="58470135f336ff95020023fb35a1b735">
      <span data-card-type="inline" data-lake-card="image" class="lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom"><img loading="lazy" data-role="image" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/gif/272392/1618189293765-1e9e9e07-0c25-4431-80ca-b8f979acda1b.gif" data-raw-src="" class="image lake-drag-image" alt="可见性表达式_表单.gif" title="可见性表达式_表单.gif" data-height="244px"/>
      </span>
    </p>
    <p data-lake-id="8da258aaeebd393bdd210117fbb18884">
      可以看到，根据选择的形状不同，显示了不同的尺寸参数。
    </p>
    <p data-lake-id="ac9cf6ea52dbe139241601da98614863">
      在定义表单时，“宽度”和“高度”字段，在“形状”选择“长方形”时显示。对应的可见性表达式如下图所示：
    </p>
    <p data-lake-id="9a9774eea2d6c87352d12eba5d6dc082">
      <span data-card-type="inline" data-lake-card="image" class="lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom"><img loading="lazy" data-role="image" src="https://files.getquicker.net/_sitefiles/kc/yuque/0/2021/png/272392/1618189417882-603ffe7b-331b-456e-b9ef-75acea6f822e.png" data-raw-src="" class="image lake-drag-image" alt="image.png" title="image.png" data-height="358px"/>
</span>    </p>
